{"tid":1948762,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"富臨旗下8間陶源酒家今起暫停晚市14日","createTime":"2020-03-29T08:15:49.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-29T08:16:40.000Z","uid":64603,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"f66578c8a9a96764691632e1fa9a0e6b50134323","tid":1948762,"uid":64603,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T08:15:49.000Z","msg":"富臨集團旗下8間陶源酒家今日起暫停晚市14日，另外4間富臨酒家繼續休業。<br />\n<br />\n富臨集團表示，新型肺炎確診個案持續增加，為配合政府推出的新規例，期望暫停晚市及休業，有助減少人群聚集及社區爆發的機會。<br />\n<br />\n8間暫停晚市服務的陶源酒家分別位於灣仔、黃埔、旺角、九龍灣、國際廣場、奧海城、觀塘及荃灣沙咀道，4間繼續休業的富臨酒家則位於香港仔、北角、上水等。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1517562-20200329.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1517562-20200329.htm&d=XV0%2F%2BsWk6HIEEz5%2BsPHJexYTjY4AGk5vqx1zl%2FZrtgc%3D&h=d53ac9c8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1517562-20200329.htm&h=5c17aaea\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1517562-20200329.htm</a>"},{"pid":"68f7708b1a45d742649e53d52a339845a0977838","tid":1948762,"uid":64603,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T08:16:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MaernmO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMaernmO.jpg&h=f49842f2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6bb119bbd4705591a0545a3ee02dfc8e1840ac73","tid":1948762,"uid":41389,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T08:16:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}